<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
  <title>CDA Lake Trout ‚Äî Oven ‚Ä¢ Grill ‚Ä¢ Pan (v2 Interactive Guide)</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Interactive how-to for fresh-caught trout from Coeur d'Alene Lake: oven, grill, pan. Timers, flavor paths, serving scaler, story mode, print mode." />

  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#071622;
      --panel:#0b2233;
      --panel2:#0d2a40;
      --text:#e9f3ff;
      --muted:#a9c3da;
      --accent:#7fe7ff;
      --accent2:#8bffb0;
      --warn:#ffd27f;
      --hot:#ff7f9a;
      --line:rgba(127,231,255,.18);
      --shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.35);
      --radius: 18px;
      --mono: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Liberation Mono","Courier New", monospace;
      --sans: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, "Apple Color Emoji","Segoe UI Emoji";
      --tap: 44px;
    }
    *{box-sizing:border-box}
    html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
    body{
      margin:0;
      font-family:var(--sans);
      color:var(--text);
      background:
        radial-gradient(1100px 700px at 18% 10%, rgba(127,231,255,.12), transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(900px 500px at 82% 20%, rgba(139,255,176,.10), transparent 55%),
        radial-gradient(1200px 800px at 50% 110%, rgba(255,127,154,.08), transparent 55%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #06121c, #071622 35%, #06111a);
      min-height:100vh;
      overflow-x:hidden;
    }
    a{color:var(--accent)}
    .wrap{max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:16px 14px 86px}

    /* Accessibility */
    .skip{
      position:absolute; left:-9999px; top:10px;
      background:#fff; color:#000;
      padding:10px 12px; border-radius:10px;
      z-index:9999;
    }
    .skip:focus{left:10px}

    header.hero{
      margin-top:8px;
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(15,55,82,.55), rgba(10,34,51,.35));
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:var(--radius);
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      padding:16px 16px 14px;
      position:relative;
      overflow:hidden;
    }
    .topRow{display:flex; gap:16px; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap}
    .badge{
      display:inline-flex; gap:8px; align-items:center;
      padding:7px 11px;
      border:1px solid rgba(127,231,255,.22);
      background:rgba(127,231,255,.08);
      border-radius:999px;
      font-family:var(--mono);
      font-size:12px;
      letter-spacing:.3px;
      color:var(--muted);
      white-space:nowrap;
    }
    h1{margin:10px 0 6px; font-size:clamp(26px, 3.2vw, 44px); line-height:1.08; letter-spacing:-.6px}
    .sub{margin:0; color:var(--muted); max-width:75ch; line-height:1.55; font-size:15px}

    /* Sticky top bar */
    .bar{
      position:sticky;
      top:0;
      z-index:999;
      margin-top:12px;
      border-radius:var(--radius);
      border:1px solid rgba(127,231,255,.18);
      background:rgba(6,18,28,.68);
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.25);
      overflow:hidden;
    }
    .barRow{
      display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:10px;
      padding:10px 10px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
    }
    .tabs{display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap}
    .tab{
      min-height: var(--tap);
      display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
      padding:10px 12px;
      border-radius:999px;
      text-decoration:none;
      color:var(--text);
      border:1px solid rgba(169,195,218,.18);
      background:rgba(11,34,51,.55);
      transition: transform .14s ease, border-color .14s ease, background .14s ease;
      font-size:14px;
      user-select:none;
    }
    .tab:hover{transform: translateY(-1px); border-color:rgba(127,231,255,.34); background:rgba(11,34,51,.75)}
    .tab[aria-current="true"]{
      border-color: rgba(127,231,255,.55);
      background: rgba(127,231,255,.12);
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(127,231,255,.18);
    }
    .controls{display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap; align-items:center}
    .btn{
      min-height: var(--tap);
      padding:10px 12px;
      border-radius:12px;
      border:1px solid rgba(169,195,218,.18);
      background:rgba(11,34,51,.55);
      color:var(--text);
      cursor:pointer;
      font-size:14px;
      display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
      transition: transform .14s ease, border-color .14s ease, background .14s ease;
      user-select:none;
    }
    .btn:hover{transform: translateY(-1px); border-color:rgba(127,231,255,.34); background:rgba(11,34,51,.75)}
    .btn.primary{border-color:rgba(127,231,255,.45); background:rgba(127,231,255,.10)}
    .tog{
      display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
      padding:6px 10px;
      border-radius:999px;
      border:1px solid rgba(169,195,218,.18);
      background:rgba(11,34,51,.35);
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:12.5px;
      user-select:none;
      min-height: var(--tap);
    }
    .tog input{accent-color: var(--accent)}
    .tog b{color:var(--text); font-weight:600}

    /* Layout */
    .grid{
      margin-top:16px;
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr .8fr;
      gap:14px;
      align-items:stretch;
    }
    @media (max-width: 980px){ .grid{grid-template-columns:1fr} }

    .card{
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(11,34,51,.78), rgba(9,26,39,.62));
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:var(--radius);
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      overflow:hidden;
    }
    .cardHeader{
      padding:14px 16px 12px;
      border-bottom:1px solid rgba(127,231,255,.14);
      display:flex; align-items:flex-start; justify-content:space-between; gap:12px;
    }
    .cardHeader h2{margin:0; font-size:18px; letter-spacing:-.2px}
    .hint{
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:12px;
      font-family:var(--mono);
      padding:6px 10px;
      border:1px dashed rgba(169,195,218,.22);
      border-radius:999px;
      white-space:nowrap;
    }
    .cardBody{padding:14px 16px 16px}
    .twoCol{display:grid; gap:12px; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr}
    @media (max-width: 760px){ .twoCol{grid-template-columns:1fr} }

    .box{
      border:1px solid rgba(169,195,218,.16);
      background:rgba(6,18,28,.35);
      border-radius:14px;
      padding:12px 12px 10px;
    }
    .box h3{margin:0 0 8px; font-size:14px; color:var(--accent); letter-spacing:.2px}
    ul{margin:8px 0 0 20px;padding:0}
    li{margin:6px 0; line-height:1.45}
    .muted{color:var(--muted)}
    .fine{font-size:12.5px; color:var(--muted); line-height:1.55}
    .kbd{
      font-family:var(--mono);
      font-size:12px;
      border:1px solid rgba(169,195,218,.22);
      padding:6px 9px;
      border-radius:10px;
      background:rgba(11,34,51,.35);
      color:var(--muted);
      white-space:nowrap;
    }

    /* Details accordion */
    details{
      border:1px solid rgba(169,195,218,.16);
      background:rgba(6,18,28,.30);
      border-radius:14px;
      padding:8px 10px;
      overflow:hidden;
    }
    summary{
      cursor:pointer;
      user-select:none;
      list-style:none;
      display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:10px;
      min-height: var(--tap);
      padding:6px 6px;
    }
    summary::-webkit-details-marker{display:none}
    .sumTitle{display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; font-weight:650}
    .chip{
      font-family:var(--mono);
      font-size:12px;
      color:var(--muted);
      border:1px solid rgba(169,195,218,.18);
      background:rgba(11,34,51,.35);
      padding:4px 8px;
      border-radius:999px;
      white-space:nowrap;
    }
    .chev{
      width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:12px;
      border:1px solid rgba(169,195,218,.18);
      display:grid; place-items:center;
      background:rgba(11,34,51,.35);
      transition: transform .15s ease;
      flex:0 0 auto;
    }
    details[open] .chev{transform: rotate(180deg)}
    .detailsBody{padding:8px 6px 10px}

    /* Method section */
    section.method{scroll-margin-top:88px}
    .methodTitle{display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin:0}
    .tag{
      display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;
      padding:7px 10px;
      border-radius:999px;
      border:1px solid rgba(169,195,218,.18);
      background:rgba(6,18,28,.22);
      font-family:var(--mono);
      font-size:12px;
      color:var(--muted);
    }
    .tag .dot{
      width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;
      background:var(--accent);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(127,231,255,.12);
    }
    .tag.hot .dot{background:var(--hot); box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(255,127,154,.12)}
    .tag.green .dot{background:var(--accent2); box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(139,255,176,.12)}

    /* Steps */
    .steps{counter-reset: step; display:grid; gap:10px; margin-top:10px}
    .step{
      display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:flex-start;
      padding:11px 12px;
      border-radius:14px;
      border:1px solid rgba(127,231,255,.14);
      background:rgba(11,34,51,.35);
    }
    .step::before{
      counter-increment: step;
      content: counter(step);
      flex:0 0 auto;
      width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:10px;
      display:grid;place-items:center;
      background:rgba(127,231,255,.14);
      border:1px solid rgba(127,231,255,.22);
      font-family:var(--mono);
      color:var(--accent);
      font-size:12px;
    }
    .step p{margin:0; line-height:1.5}

    /* Callout */
    .callout{
      border:1px solid rgba(255,210,127,.18);
      background:rgba(255,210,127,.08);
      border-radius:14px;
      padding:12px;
      margin-top:12px;
    }
    .callout b{color:var(--warn)}

    /* Flavor paths */
    .flavorGrid{display:grid; gap:10px; grid-template-columns:repeat(2, 1fr)}
    @media (max-width:760px){ .flavorGrid{grid-template-columns:1fr} }

    .flavor{
      border:1px solid rgba(127,231,255,.16);
      background:rgba(6,18,28,.26);
      border-radius:14px;
      padding:12px;
      cursor:pointer;
      transition: transform .14s ease, border-color .14s ease, background .14s ease;
      min-height: var(--tap);
    }
    .flavor:hover{transform: translateY(-1px); border-color:rgba(127,231,255,.34); background:rgba(6,18,28,.36)}
    .flavor[aria-selected="true"]{
      border-color:rgba(127,231,255,.55);
      background:rgba(127,231,255,.10);
      box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(127,231,255,.16);
    }
    .flavor h4{margin:0 0 6px; font-size:15px}
    .flavor .desc{margin:0; color:var(--muted); font-size:13px; line-height:1.45}
    .flavor .mini{margin-top:8px; display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap}
    .pillMini{
      font-family:var(--mono);
      font-size:12px;
      padding:4px 8px;
      border-radius:999px;
      border:1px solid rgba(169,195,218,.18);
      background:rgba(11,34,51,.35);
      color:var(--muted);
      white-space:nowrap;
    }

    /* Timer */
    .timerRow{display:flex; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap; align-items:center}
    .timerDisplay{
      font-family:var(--mono);
      font-size:14px;
      border:1px solid rgba(169,195,218,.18);
      background:rgba(11,34,51,.35);
      padding:10px 12px;
      border-radius:12px;
      min-height: var(--tap);
      display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;
    }
    .timerBtns{display:flex; gap:8px; flex-wrap:wrap}
    .timerBtns .btn{border-radius:999px}
    .toast{
      position:fixed;
      left:12px; right:12px; bottom:12px;
      max-width:720px; margin:0 auto;
      background:rgba(6,18,28,.78);
      border:1px solid rgba(127,231,255,.22);
      border-radius:16px;
      padding:12px 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.35);
      display:none;
      z-index:1200;
      backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
    }
    .toast.show{display:block}
    .toastTop{display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; gap:10px}
    .toastTitle{font-weight:700}
    .toastMsg{margin:6px 0 0; color:var(--muted); font-size:13px; line-height:1.45}
    .x{border-radius:12px}

    /* Mascot + section icons */
    .mascot{
      width:260px; max-width:100%;
      aspect-ratio: 13 / 6;
      border-radius:16px;
      border:1px solid rgba(127,231,255,.18);
      background:rgba(6,18,28,.22);
      overflow:hidden;
      position:relative;
      transform: translateZ(0);
    }
    .mascot svg{width:100%;height:100%;display:block}
    .swim{animation: swim 3.8s ease-in-out infinite; transform-origin: 40% 50%;}
    @keyframes swim{0%,100%{transform: translateX(-2px) rotate(-1deg)}50%{transform: translateX(8px) rotate(1.5deg)}}
    .tail{animation: wag .45s ease-in-out infinite; transform-origin: 78% 50%;}
    @keyframes wag{0%,100%{transform: rotate(10deg)}50%{transform: rotate(-12deg)}}
    .spark{animation: sparkle 2.4s ease-in-out infinite; transform-origin:center; opacity:.55;}
    .spark:nth-child(2){animation-delay:-.8s}
    .spark:nth-child(3){animation-delay:-1.6s}
    @keyframes sparkle{0%,100%{transform: scale(.92); opacity:.30}50%{transform: scale(1.05); opacity:.70}}

    /* Method micro-animations */
    .iconRow{display:flex; gap:10px; flex-wrap:wrap; align-items:center}
    .iconBadge{
      display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;
      padding:10px 12px;
      border-radius:14px;
      border:1px solid rgba(169,195,218,.18);
      background:rgba(6,18,28,.24);
    }
    .ico{width:36px;height:36px}
    .heatWave path{animation: wave 1.7s ease-in-out infinite; opacity:.8}
    .heatWave path:nth-child(2){animation-delay:-.6s; opacity:.65}
    .heatWave path:nth-child(3){animation-delay:-1.1s; opacity:.55}
    @keyframes wave{0%,100%{transform:translateY(0)}50%{transform:translateY(-3px)}}
    .smoke{animation: smoke 2.2s ease-in-out infinite; transform-origin:center; opacity:.8}
    @keyframes smoke{0%{transform:translateY(2px) scale(.98); opacity:.25}50%{transform:translateY(-3px) scale(1.02); opacity:.65}100%{transform:translateY(-6px) scale(1.03); opacity:.0}}
    .sizzle circle{animation: pop 1.6s ease-in-out infinite; opacity:.55}
    .sizzle circle:nth-child(2){animation-delay:-.45s}
    .sizzle circle:nth-child(3){animation-delay:-.9s}
    @keyframes pop{0%,100%{transform:translateY(0) scale(.92); opacity:.25}55%{transform:translateY(-4px) scale(1.05); opacity:.75}}

    /* Story mode + compact mode */
    .story{display:none}
    body.storyMode .story{display:block}
    body.compactMode .story{display:none}
    body.compactMode .fine{display:none}
    body.compactMode .hint{display:none}

    /* Print */
    @media print{
      html{scroll-behavior:auto}
      body{background:#fff;color:#111}
      .bar,.toast{display:none !important}
      header.hero,.card{box-shadow:none}
      .card{border-color:#ddd;background:#fff}
      .box,details{border-color:#e6e6e6;background:#fafafa}
      .step{border-color:#e6e6e6;background:#fff}
      a{color:#0b6}
      .mascot{display:none}
    }

    /* Reduced motion */
    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){
      html{scroll-behavior:auto}
      .swim,.tail,.spark,.heatWave path,.smoke,.sizzle circle{animation:none !important}
      .tab,.btn,.flavor{transition:none !important}
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <a class="skip" href="#main">Skip to content</a>

  <div class="wrap">
    <header class="hero" aria-label="CDA Lake trout guide header">
      <div class="topRow">
        <div class="mascot" title="Official Coeur d'Alene Lake Trout Inspector (self-appointed)">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 520 240" aria-label="Animated trout mascot">
            <defs>
              <linearGradient id="gWater" x1="0" x2="1">
                <stop offset="0" stop-color="rgba(127,231,255,.14)"/>
                <stop offset="1" stop-color="rgba(139,255,176,.10)"/>
              </linearGradient>
              <linearGradient id="gFish" x1="0" x2="1">
                <stop offset="0" stop-color="#b7f2ff"/>
                <stop offset="1" stop-color="#6fd6ff"/>
              </linearGradient>
              <linearGradient id="gFin" x1="0" x2="1">
                <stop offset="0" stop-color="#8bffb0"/>
                <stop offset="1" stop-color="#7fe7ff"/>
              </linearGradient>
            </defs>

            <rect x="0" y="0" width="520" height="240" fill="url(#gWater)"/>
            <path d="M0,150 C80,130 130,170 210,150 C300,125 350,180 520,145 L520,240 L0,240 Z"
                  fill="rgba(7,22,34,.35)"/>

            <g class="spark">
              <circle cx="70" cy="60" r="4" fill="rgba(127,231,255,.65)"/>
              <circle cx="92" cy="78" r="2.5" fill="rgba(139,255,176,.6)"/>
            </g>
            <g class="spark">
              <circle cx="440" cy="62" r="4" fill="rgba(127,231,255,.55)"/>
              <circle cx="462" cy="84" r="2.6" fill="rgba(255,127,154,.5)"/>
            </g>
            <g class="spark">
              <circle cx="310" cy="44" r="3.4" fill="rgba(139,255,176,.55)"/>
              <circle cx="332" cy="64" r="2.2" fill="rgba(127,231,255,.5)"/>
            </g>

            <g class="swim" transform="translate(40,20)">
              <ellipse cx="240" cy="115" rx="150" ry="55" fill="url(#gFish)" opacity=".95"/>
              <ellipse cx="260" cy="112" rx="110" ry="38" fill="rgba(7,22,34,.12)"/>

              <g opacity=".35">
                <circle cx="190" cy="110" r="5" fill="rgba(7,22,34,.35)"/>
                <circle cx="225" cy="92" r="4" fill="rgba(7,22,34,.35)"/>
                <circle cx="255" cy="122" r="3.8" fill="rgba(7,22,34,.35)"/>
                <circle cx="290" cy="98" r="4.4" fill="rgba(7,22,34,.35)"/>
                <circle cx="320" cy="120" r="3.5" fill="rgba(7,22,34,.35)"/>
              </g>

              <ellipse cx="130" cy="118" rx="55" ry="42" fill="url(#gFish)"/>
              <circle cx="110" cy="110" r="7" fill="rgba(7,22,34,.75)"/>
              <circle cx="108" cy="108" r="2.5" fill="rgba(255,255,255,.8)"/>
              <path d="M90,130 C110,142 128,142 148,130" fill="none" stroke="rgba(7,22,34,.45)" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round"/>

              <path d="M220,72 C250,90 270,90 300,72 C290,105 250,110 220,72 Z" fill="url(#gFin)" opacity=".9"/>

              <g class="tail">
                <path d="M385,115 L455,75 L438,120 L455,165 L385,115 Z" fill="url(#gFin)" opacity=".92"/>
                <path d="M395,115 L445,92" stroke="rgba(7,22,34,.18)" stroke-width="5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                <path d="M395,115 L445,138" stroke="rgba(7,22,34,.18)" stroke-width="5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
              </g>
            </g>

            <text x="18" y="226" font-family="ui-monospace, Menlo, Consolas, monospace" font-size="12"
                  fill="rgba(233,243,255,.75)">
              ‚ÄúI was THIS close to becoming a legend.‚Äù ‚Äî Trout (probably)
            </text>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <div style="flex:1 1 480px; min-width:260px;">
          <div class="badge">CDA LAKE ‚Ä¢ FRESH CATCH ‚Ä¢ v2 INTERACTIVE ‚Ä¢ TIMERS + FLAVORS</div>
          <h1>Cook Fresh-Caught Trout: Oven ‚Ä¢ Grill ‚Ä¢ Pan</h1>
          <p class="sub">
            This page is built like a little lake-side field manual: pick a <b>method</b>, pick a <b>flavor path</b>,
            set your <b>servings</b>, and tap a <b>timer</b>. You‚Äôll get dinner fast ‚Äî with just enough story to keep it fun.
          </p>
          <p class="story fine" style="margin-top:10px">
            Story mode: imagine you‚Äôre back at Coeur d‚ÄôAlene Lake, telling someone about ‚Äúthe one that almost got away,‚Äù
            while your kitchen smells like victory. We‚Äôre not saying that‚Äôs required‚Ä¶ but it‚Äôs encouraged.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Sticky Bar -->
    <nav class="bar" aria-label="Section navigation and controls">
      <div class="barRow">
        <div class="tabs" role="tablist" aria-label="Sections">
          <a class="tab" href="#basics" data-spy="basics" role="tab">üßº Basics</a>
          <a class="tab" href="#choose" data-spy="choose" role="tab">üé£ Choose Fish</a>
          <a class="tab" href="#flavors" data-spy="flavors" role="tab">üß™ Flavor Paths</a>
          <a class="tab" href="#oven" data-spy="oven" role="tab">üî• Oven</a>
          <a class="tab" href="#grill" data-spy="grill" role="tab">‚ô®Ô∏è Grill</a>
          <a class="tab" href="#pan" data-spy="pan" role="tab">üç≥ Pan</a>
          <a class="tab" href="#sides" data-spy="sides" role="tab">ü•ó Sides</a>
        </div>

        <div class="controls">
          <label class="tog" title="Scale ingredient amounts">
            <span>Servings:</span>
            <b id="servingsLabel">2</b>
            <input id="servings" type="range" min="1" max="6" value="2" aria-label="Servings slider" />
